.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-9::.
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, canadian, australian, turkish
1. the australian is on the far left or far right##3
2. the turkish is somewhere to the right of the indonesian##5
3. the canadian is on the right of the turkish##1
4. the turkish is somewhere between the canadian and the australian##7

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |  3  |    4    |
| Nationality   | australian | indonesian | turkish | canadian |

