.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-7-10::.
House: modern, gothic-revival, cape-cod, palace
1. the modern house is somewhere between the palace house and the gothic-revival house##7
2. the cape-cod house is on the left of the modern house##1
3. the gothic-revival house is on the left of the cape-cod house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| House   | gothic-revival | cape-cod | modern | palace |

